// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2362 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 9a82e99a-62ac-54c8-98dd-043d18d8af41

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
